HEADWORD: Marrowbone
<hw>Mar"row*bone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A bone
containing marrow;</def> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <def>ludicrously, knee bones
or knees; <as>as, to get down on one's <ex>marrowbones</ex>, <it>i.
